# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:9
translate chinese mills2_bf62d9d2:

    # "I go into Mrs. Mills office and start working for the day, beginning with dusting and cleaning."
    "我走进米尔斯夫人的办公室开始一天的工作，先从擦灰和打扫卫生做起。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:10
translate chinese mills2_9280c256:

    # "It doesn't take long before I feel her eyes watching me."
    "没过多久，我就感觉到她的目光在注视着我。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:12
translate chinese mills2_72f88165:

    # "She lets out a long sigh."
    "她长长地叹了口气。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:13
translate chinese mills2_a9f9f8cf:

    # pc "Something wrong?"
    pc "有什么事吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:16
translate chinese mills2_69c5abb5:

    # bs "I really shouldn't even be talking to you about it."
    bs "我其实根本不该跟你谈这个的。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:17
translate chinese mills2_e2897626:

    # pc "It's okay. I don't mind and I won't tell anybody."
    pc "没关系。我不介意，也不会告诉任何人。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:18
translate chinese mills2_945e9f67:

    # bs "Well see, my personal trainer is out of town."
    bs "是这样的，我的私人教练出城了。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:19
translate chinese mills2_4c900a01:

    # bs "And we've had a thing going on for a while, where he comes over, helps me work out..."
    bs "我们有一阵子在搞暧昧，他会过来帮我锻炼……"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:20
translate chinese mills2_1a25acb0:

    # bs "Then he relaxes me by giving me some good dick."
    bs "然后他会用那玩意儿让我放松下来。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:21
translate chinese mills2_f151517c:

    # pc "Uh..."
    pc "呃……"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:22
translate chinese mills2_63029bd2:

    # bs "But since he's gone for the week, I haven't been able to get any and I'm feeling a little pent up, you know?"
    bs "但因为他这周不在，我都没能得到满足，感觉有点憋着，你知道的？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:24
translate chinese mills2_0110cdb8:

    # bs "I'm just craving it."
    bs "我就是特别想要。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:30
translate chinese mills2_c793b45c:

    # bs "Right. You're right. I'm sorry."
    bs "对。你说得对。对不起。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:31
translate chinese mills2_a346dca8:

    # bs "I won't bring it up again. Back to work [pcname]."
    bs "我以后不会再提这事了。回去工作吧[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:33
translate chinese mills2_09914973:

    # "I go back to what I had been doing and Mrs. Mills goes back to working at her desk. We don't talk any more the rest of the day."
    "我继续做手头的事，米尔斯太太也回到了她的办公桌前。那天剩下的时间里，我们再没说过话。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:36
translate chinese mills2_5e9ea2bc:

    # "I drive home, thinking that I could have maybe done something with Mrs. Mills, but it hadn't felt right."
    "我开车回家，心想或许可以和米尔斯太太发生点什么，但总觉得不太对劲。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:37
translate chinese mills2_64e0e1c1:

    # "She is my boss and I don't want to get in any sort of relationship with her past that."
    "她是我的老板，我不想和她发展任何超越职场的关系。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:43
translate chinese mills2_76f8dc88:

    # bs "Oh yeah?"
    bs "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:44
translate chinese mills2_46f44fb2:

    # bs "You'd like that?"
    bs "你想那样吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:46
translate chinese mills2_d529cf63:

    # bs "I bet you would like that. You'd like being my little fuckboy?"
    bs "我敢打赌你肯定想。你想当我的小情郎吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:47
translate chinese mills2_1ca45f42:

    # pc "Well, yeah."
    pc "嗯，是啊。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:48
translate chinese mills2_92bc68f0:

    # bs "I'd be lying if I said that I haven't thought about it."
    bs "如果我说没想过，那是在撒谎。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:50
translate chinese mills2_a81d699f:

    # bs "I am curious as to how you would be, since you're so young."
    bs "我很想知道你会是什么样子，毕竟你这么年轻。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:51
translate chinese mills2_262400a9:

    # bs "I've had younger lovers in the past, but none quite as young as you."
    bs "我以前也有过更年轻的情人，但没一个像你这么年轻。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:52
translate chinese mills2_29cb0621:

    # bs "I bet you could fuck all night, couldn't you?"
    bs "我打赌你能整晚做爱，对吧？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:53
translate chinese mills2_f29db352:

    # pc "Sure. Any time."
    pc "当然。随时都可以。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:55
translate chinese mills2_493e0d50:

    # bs "You are tempting, that is for sure."
    bs "你确实很诱人，这一点毋庸置疑。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:57
translate chinese mills2_289f1f92:

    # bs "But I'm your boss and we shouldn't complicate that relationship."
    bs "但我可是你的老板，我们不该让这段关系变得复杂。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:58
translate chinese mills2_fefc9af5:

    # bs "If I wore you out by fucking you all the time, who would clean my office?"
    bs "如果我整天跟你做爱把你搞垮了，谁来打扫我的办公室？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:59
translate chinese mills2_56781dd8:

    # bs "I'll just wait for my personal trainer to get back from his vacation."
    bs "我就等着我的私人教练度假回来吧。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:60
translate chinese mills2_e91981f0:

    # pc "Okay, Mrs. Mills, but you're missing out."
    pc "好吧，米尔斯夫人，但你可是错过了好机会。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:62
translate chinese mills2_0cd671b4:

    # "When I turn around to start cleaning, she slaps me on my ass hard."
    "当我转身开始打扫时，她狠狠地拍了拍我的屁股。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:63
translate chinese mills2_362a9366:

    # bs "Get back to work, fuckboy."
    bs "回去干活，小色鬼。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:65
translate chinese mills2_1da8b21d:

    # "I do as she said and go back to cleaning the office."
    "我照她说的做了，回去打扫办公室。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:66
translate chinese mills2_cbbe4d0e:

    # "The whole time, I am distracted by Mrs. Mills."
    "整个过程中，我的心思都飘到了米尔斯太太身上。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:67
translate chinese mills2_7e488788:

    # "She had thought about having sex with me. She is probably thinking about it right now."
    "她曾想过和我上床。她现在八成也在想这件事。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:68
translate chinese mills2_e6e97d64:

    # "I am pretty sure she wants me just as bad as I want her."
    "我敢肯定，她想要我的程度，和我想要她的程度一样强烈。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:69
translate chinese mills2_1fae0581:

    # "I just need a little time and I'm sure I can make it happen. I am going to fuck my boss."
    "我只需要一点时间，我相信一定能成事。我要和我的老板上床。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:70
translate chinese mills2_82973669:

    # "Fantasies of how it would happen spin through my head the rest of the day, until it is time to close up and leave."
    "接下来的时间里，关于这会如何发生的幻想在我脑海中盘旋，直到打烊下班的时候。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:73
translate chinese mills2_bbf9ce82:

    # bs "Good work today. You have a good night."
    bs "今天干得不错。晚安。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:74
translate chinese mills2_27ed6fe0:

    # pc "Thanks, Mrs. Mills. You too."
    pc "谢谢，米尔斯夫人。你也一样。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:78
translate chinese mills2_79fa28af:

    # bs "I'll see you Monday, fuckboy."
    bs "周一见，小色鬼。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:81
translate chinese mills2_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/mills_seeyoutomorrow.mp3'
    voice 'voices/mills_seeyoutomorrow.mp3'

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:82
translate chinese mills2_c73888a8:

    # bs "I'll see you tomorrow, fuckboy."
    bs "明天见，小色鬼。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills2.rpy:83
translate chinese mills2_d77b84eb:

    # "I leave and head out to my car."
    "我离开，走向自己的车。"

